{"tid":895921,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗仔離開左我 心情完全平伏唔到","createTime":"2018-11-09T14:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T04:22:43.000Z","uid":53803,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd47a46e0b679deaee076f1f49d6c98a049d0e4","tid":895921,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"上個星期仲好開心咁周圍走<br />\n大前日大便有血 即刻入院<br />\n吊左兩三日鹽水 原來個腎已經衰竭 救唔翻<br />\n見到佢咁痛苦...寧願今晚比佢安安樂樂<br />\n好過再留係醫院受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩陪到佢最後一刻<br />\n個人直情係崩潰狀態<br />\n不停喊 不停喊.....<br />\n原來佢已經陪左我十幾年....<br />\n<br />\n各位養緊狗仔貓仔嘅巴絲<br />\n希望你地好好痛錫自己嘅仔仔女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2fb4be99285c4216cf98891774a762020a1c7b","tid":895921,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"我明白 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84029d8a4e24cc63d6eade8e5895cca91f5c351","tid":895921,"uid":217437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"好明白樓主感受 所以唔會再養寵物啦"},{"pid":"fd453c63f08778aa37a5fdb77038813afe99661a","tid":895921,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"慘慘"},{"pid":"5498e775ceea61376b319b9ff87182c958fb9025","tid":895921,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"節哀順變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b9a15fc4e85f336570fc1ebdacb17b4d66a4fd","tid":895921,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"3bb0bc23118cfb2f713fad52f7a3a5806d0f7c9d","tid":895921,"uid":53803,"like":0,